snippet.title: Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt: Kimmy vs. The Reverend | Interactive Special Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Kimmy sets off on her biggest adventure yet. Three states! Explosions! A dancing hamburger! And you, the viewer, get to decide how the story goes. 

Watch Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt: Kimmy vs. The Reverend, only on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81131714

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7
